<!-- Sub-descriptor loaded only when `com.intellij.modules.jcef` is present (2026.2+).

     Its contents mirror conan-clion-plugin's withJcef.xml verbatim — the only known precedent that actually fixed
     this same crash on 2026.2 (commit ab66c80a, 2026-07-20). Reading platform source suggests this <dependencies>
     block is inert inside a `depends` sub-descriptor (moduleDependencies is set to EMPTY there) and that the
     <depends optional> line in the main descriptor is what does the work. That reading is unverified, though, and
     the cost of omitting the block is a fix that fails silently on 2026.2 — precisely the end we cannot observe.
     So we copy the combination known to work rather than simplify it. -->
<idea-plugin>
    <dependencies>
        <module name="intellij.platform.ui.jcef"/>
    </dependencies>
</idea-plugin>
